additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Will irritate the eyes. May irritate the skin. Avoid contact with eyes and skin. Do not inhale spray mist. Wash hands after use. Discontinue wearing treated garment if skin irritation occurs. Do not spray towards face. Do not spray directly onto humans, pets, exposed food, water, food preparation areas or food utensils. Very toxic to aquatic life. Do not throw product into waterways. Ecotoxic to bees. Do not use near bees. Care should be taken when spraying delicate fabrics and furnishings. Remove or cover fish tanks before spraying.
